381
00:27:54,537 --> 00:27:57,540
Anda boleh memberi penghormatan
tanpa rasa terganggu dengan kehadiran saya.

382
00:27:58,165 --> 00:27:59,250
Jumpa di sekolah.

383
00:27:59,834 --> 00:28:03,588
Kenapa Maggie benci awak sampai habis?

384
